  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00114', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-113-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '若船舶駕駛台當值人員看到人員於右舷側落水時，駕駛台當值甲級船員應轉滿舵角向  ①  舷側，以利用', '["現象，使船艉遠離落水人員。試問", "、", "應為下列何項？", "左、橫移"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b14ecfcba47e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7eb32a391986", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "161", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00115', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-113-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '以一般航行經驗值之估算，船舶在淺水區域航行時，船體下沉量（以公尺計）與下列何者成正比？', '["吃水", "船寬", "船速", "船速的平方"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b14ecfcba47e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7eb32a391986", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "161", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00116', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-113-606c6876', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '兩船相互接近航行時，將使彼此偏離航向或迴轉，此現象稱為兩船間的相互作用（Interaction）。關於兩 船相互作用大小之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["船速愈大時愈大", "反向航行時較同向航行時之影響為大", "兩船接近距離愈小，則相互作用力愈大", "在大小兩船間，小型船之一方所受之影響較大"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b14ecfcba47e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7eb32a391986", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "161", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航行當值大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL)
